      "activeWorkerNodeMapByInfrastructureWorkerCount": "Infrastructure-level placement mapping keyed by the number of Kubernetes worker nodes available in the generated cluster. This is the canonical map for provider-backed node-count and placement analyses across two-, three- and four-worker-node infrastructures."
